item.title: CVE-2021-39312|2024-08-04T02:06:41.997Z -- true%20ranker -- true%20ranker
item.description: The True Ranker plugin <= 2.2.2 for WordPress allows arbitrary files, including sensitive configuration files such as wp-config.php, to be accessed via the src parameter found in the ~/admin/vendor/datatables/examples/resources/examples.php file.
